    "synopsis": "Six short stories about the men the Emperor made to be His sons. A weak Cthonian boy carves a place for himself in the underhives of the gang world and steps onto the path that becomes Horus. Tribal hunters track a beast through Fenrisian snows under a yellow-eyed leader who is more than he seems. Prosperine sorcerers reach for a secret their lord has forbidden them. The Emperor's praetorian shows the side of Rogal Dorn most do not survive. Alpharius submits to questioning over a brutal compliance and gives nothing away. And after his fall, Mortarion comes home to Terra for the first time as a daemon prince.",
